  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nI believe we're being dropped by lighthouse because we don't 'support' gossipsub until we get past initial sync.\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nWe should start gossipsub **but not subscribe to any topics** on network start.\r\nThen when we finish initial sync, we can subscribe to topics.\r\nThis will allow us to stay connected to clients which require peers to be gossipsub peers while we sync.\r\n",
